Installation & Setup
Step 1: Clone Repository
git clone https://github.com/AbhiramChowdhary/TalentScout-AI.git
cd TalentScout-AI
Step 2: Set Up MySQL Database
mysql -u root -p
Then run:

CREATE DATABASE catalyst_ai;
USE catalyst_ai;

